er burst from the snow and ice to attack me.\n\nNaturally, I ran like hell. The creature cornered me anyway.\n\nThat's when SHE appeared, as if from nowhere \u2014 the beautiful, mysterious girl who saved my life.\n\nShe told me her name was Kuon. A beautiful, mysterious girl...\n\n...with a tail and ears like a beast's. \"", "summary": "Utawarerumono: Mask of Deception is a grand tale that will enchant the hearts and minds of players as it takes them on an incredible journey. With a beautiful visual novel story experience, intriguing characters, fast-paced SRPG combat, world-class soundtrack and more. The game begins atop a snowy mountain where the protagonist awakens in an unfamiliar wilderness, surrounded by deadly creatures, with nothing but a hospital gown and a splitting headache. However, he's rescued by a beautiful girl named Kuon, who sports both adorable animal ears and a beastlike tail. Finding that the hapless man has no memory of anything, Kuon decides to take the amnesiac into her care, naming him Haku.", "themes": [{"id": 1, "name": "Action"}, {"id": 17, "name": "Fantasy"}, {"id": 31, "name": "Drama"}, {"id": 39, "name": "Warfare"}], "url": "https://www.igdb.com/games/utawarerumono-mask-of-deception", "videos": [{"id": 15706, "name": "Trailer", "video_id": "BL7zNEGyqCY", "url": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=BL7zNEGyqCY", "title": "Trouble Is Brewing in Utawarerumono: Mask of Deception", "thumb": "https://i.ytimg.com/vi/BL7zNEGyqCY/maxresdefault.jpg"}, {"id": 11749, "name": "Teaser", "video_id": "6kkm1GI03Ss", "url": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6kkm1GI03Ss", "title": "Adventure Awaits in Utawarerumono: Mask of Deception!", "thumb": "https://i.ytimg.com/vi/6kkm1GI03Ss/maxresdefault.jpg"}, {"id": 15707, "name": "Trailer", "video_id": "3pX4WPWYIyE", "url": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3pX4WPWYIyE", "title": "Embark on an Enchanting Adventure in Utawarerumono: Mask of Deception", "thumb": "https://i.ytimg.com/vi/3pX4WPWYIyE/maxresdefault.jpg"}]